PROJECT SETUP:
--------------
* Create a directory named "bin"
    - Create a soft symlink "bin/solr" linking to solr binary
    - Create a soft symlink "bin/trec_eval" linking to trec_eval binary
    - Create a soft symlink "bin/python" linking to python binary
* Create a directory named "symlinks"
    - Create a soft symlink "symlinks/solrdir" linking to the solr directory where the solr cores are stored
